{
  "stem": "12337.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't even know how he gave us food in those six weeks that they were there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He took such chances.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And of course my father had to empty out the pot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I don't know how-- I don't rem-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was-- it was just a miracle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was just a miracle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And of course when they retreated-- you know, the war was over, they retreated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we still-- we stayed there with him for a few weeks at least.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Because, first of all, he was afraid for his neighbors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Should they have known that they saved Jews, they would have killed him with his family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "His own neighbors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Plus the fact there were many Jews killed afterwards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "As soon as they were coming out from their hiding places into town, into [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Tuchen ?], they would be-- they would be slaughtered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he kept us for a few more weeks to make sure until things stabilized a little bit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when we crawled out from the hole.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we couldn't even walk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were holding onto sticks for support.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sorry, we had to stop for noise outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But continue with telling me when you got out of the hole.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I also want to mention before how I felt as a child in-- during the time, I was so envious of a bird outside.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- [AUDIO OUT]",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
